Feature: Checking The Hotel Booking Functionality Of Adactin Application
Scenario: Login Functionality
Given user Should Launch The URL
When user Enter The Username In Username Field
And user Enter The Password In Password Field
Then user Will Click On Login Button

Scenario: Search Hotel Functionality
When user Select The Location In The Location Field
And user Select The Hotel In The Hotel Field
And user Select The Room Type In The Room Type Field
And user Select No Of Rooms In The No Of Rooms Field
And user Select The Adults Per Room In The Adults Field
And user Select The Children Per Room In The Children Field
